<h3><br />
GoI STEPS - Schemes</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Svamitva </strong></li>
<li><strong>Digital India Land Records Modernisation Programme (DILRMP), 2008</strong></li>
<li>&nbsp;<strong>Integrated Land Information Management System (ILIMS)</strong>&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;ownership, land use, taxation, location boundaries, land value, encumbrances etc</li>
<li>&nbsp;<strong>Unique Land Parcel Identification Number (ULPIN) scheme : </strong>14-digit land aadhar</li></ol>
<p>way forward&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>Linkage of land record databases with banks - easier credit</li>
<li>Tech usage - Drones in svamitva</li></ol>